Apply Sigma Rules in Log Analysis with Chainsaw
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Install and configure Chainsaw for Windows event log analysis
Apply Sigma rules to detect security incidents in log data
Identify suspicious activities using rule-based detection
Analyze detection results and understand threat patterns
